==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: empowered
<hw>empowered</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>invested with legal
power or official authority especially as symbolized by having a
scepter.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> sceptered, sceptred.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>enabled or permitted; <as>as, the women's liberation
movement <ex>empowered</ex> wives to take more control of their own
lives</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Empress</ent>⟦br⟧
